python tricks

debug:
    import pdb
    breakpoint : pdb.set_trace()
    step in : s
    step over : n
    return out of function : r
    next breakpoint : c

LAMBDA:
>>> g = lambda x: x*2  1
>>> g(3)
6
>>> (lambda x: x*2)(3) 2
6

