    IN POWERSHELL : (Invoke-WebRequest https://bootstrap.pypa.io/ez_setup.py).Content | python -

INSTALL PACKAGES:
    PackageManager (PIP): sudo apt-get install python-pip    
    Serial: pip install pyserial